div(class="col-12 border shadow" style="background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url('https://thumbs.gfycat.com/RepentantFoolhardyHousefly-max-1mb.gif');")
  a(href="https://www.grupomave.com.br" class="d-flex flex-column bg-mave1 bg-gradient px-3" target="_blank")
    img(src=`/assets/logo.png` class="img-fluid align-self-center mt-3" style="width: 50vh;")
    h4(class="text-center text-white p-2") Você e seu patrimônio em boas mãos!
  div(class="col-12 bg-mave2 bg-gradient" style="height: 10px;")
  div(class="d-flex justify-content-center my-3 col-12")
    img(src=`/assets/perfil/avatar.png` class="rounded-circle align-self-center shadow" id="card-photo" width="180" height="180")
  div(class="d-flex flex-column my-3 col-12")
    h4(class="text-center" id="card-username") #{username || 'Nome do Colaborador'}
    h4(class="text-center" id="card-jobtitle") #{jobtitle || 'Cargo/Função'}
  div(class="d-flex justify-content-center my-3 col-12")
    div(class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-4 col-xxl-4 mx-2 p-2")
      button(type="button" class="btn btn-mave2 col-12 fs-5" id="card-phone-1" onclick="window.app.cardOpenPhone(0)") #[i(class="fas fa-phone")] #{phone_1 || '(11) 3683-3408'}
    div(class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-4 col-xxl-4 mx-2 p-2")
      button(type="button" class="btn btn-mave2 col-12 fs-5" id="card-phone-2" onclick="window.app.cardOpenPhone(1)") #[i(class="fas fa-mobile")] #{phone_2 || '(11) 99999-9999'}
  div(class="d-flex justify-content-center my-3 col-12")
    div(class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 col-xxl-6 mx-2 p-2")
      button(type="button" class="btn btn-success col-12 fs-5" id="card-phone-3" onclick="window.app.cardOpenWhatsapp(2)") #[i(class="fab fa-whatsapp")] #{phone_3 || '(11) 94784-1110'}
  div(class="d-flex justify-content-center my-3 col-12")
    div(class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 col-xxl-2 mx-2 p-2")
      button(type="button" class="btn btn-mave2 btn-sm col-12" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modalWhatsapp") #[i(class="fas fa-share-square")] Compartilhar no Whatsapp
    div(class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 col-xxl-2 mx-2 p-2")
      button(type="button" class="btn btn-mave2 btn-sm col-12" onclick="window.app.cardOpenVCF()") #[i(class="far fa-address-book")] Salvar nos contatos
  div(class="col-12 bg-mave2 bg-gradient" style="height: 10px;")
  div(class="bg-mave1 bg-gradient col-12 py-3")
    div(class="d-flex justify-content-center")
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" onclick="window.app.cardOpenMail()") #[i(class="far fa-envelope")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" onclick="window.app.cardOpenGPS()") #[i(class="fas fa-map-marked-alt")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" onclick="window.app.cardOpenWebsite()") #[i(class="fab fa-chrome")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" onclick="window.app.cardOpenFile()") #[i(class="far fa-file-pdf")]
    div(class="d-flex justify-content-center")
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" id="socialmedia-facebook" onclick="window.app.cardOpenSocialMedia('facebook')") #[i(class="fab fa-facebook")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" id="socialmedia-youtube" onclick="window.app.cardOpenSocialMedia('youtube')") #[i(class="fab fa-youtube")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" id="socialmedia-linkedin" onclick="window.app.cardOpenSocialMedia('linkedin')") #[i(class="fab fa-linkedin")]
      div(class="col-2 mx-1 p-2")
        button(type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm col-12 fs-6" id="socialmedia-instagram" onclick="window.app.cardOpenSocialMedia('instagram')") #[i(class="fab fa-instagram")]
    div(class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-2")
      div(class="col-12 text-center pt-3")
        p(class="text-white fw-bold") Grupo Mave - 2020/2021 © Todos direitos reservados.
    div(class="modal fade" id="modalWhatsapp" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="modalWhatsappLabel" aria-hidden="true")
      div(class="modal-dialog")
        div(class="modal-content bg-success bg-gradient text-white fw-bold")
          div(class="modal-header")
            h5(class="modal-title text-white" id="modalWhatsappLabel") Abra sua Agenda
            button(type="button" class="btn-close btn-light" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close")
          div(class="modal-body")
            | O whatsapp tem um limite de 5 contatos selecionados para compartilhamento por vez. #[br]
            | O link: https://grupomavedigital.com.br/cartaodigital/index, será alterado quando o cartão for criado.
          div(class="modal-footer")
            button(type="button" class="btn btn-light" data-bs-dismiss="modal" id="button-share-whatsapp")
              | Abrir
    script(src="/javascripts/public/card-layout-1.js")